<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Overlay Instructions</title>
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="16x16" href="/favicon-16.png">
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="/favicon-32.png">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <style>
    :root {
      --bg-gradient-light: linear-gradient(135deg, #4facfe, #8e44ad);
      --bg-gradient-dark: linear-gradient(135deg, #2c3e50, #000000);
      --text-color-light: white;
      --text-color-dark: #f0f0f0;
      --input-bg-dark: #333;
      --input-color-dark: #f0f0f0;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      min-height: 100vh;
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      color: var(--text-color-light);
      background: var(--bg-gradient-light);
      transition: background 0.5s, color 0.3s;
      text-align: center;
    }

    body.dark {
      background: var(--bg-gradient-dark);
      color: var(--text-color-dark);
    }

    h1 {
      margin-top: 2em;
      font-size: 2.5em;
    }

    .dark-mode-toggle {
      position: absolute;
      top: 1em;
      right: 1em;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5em;
    }

    .toggle-switch {
      position: relative;
      display: inline-block;
      width: 50px;
      height: 24px;
    }

    .toggle-switch input {
      display: none;
    }

    .slider {
      position: absolute;
      cursor: pointer;
      top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0;
      background-color: #ccc;
      transition: 0.4s;
      border-radius: 24px;
    }

    .slider:before {
      content: "‚òÄÔ∏è";
      position: absolute;
      height: 18px;
      width: 18px;
      left: 4px;
      bottom: 3px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      background-color: white;
      border-radius: 50%;
      transition: transform 0.4s, content 0.4s;
    }

    input:checked + .slider {
      background-color: #2ecc71;
    }

    input:checked + .slider:before {
      transform: translateX(26px);
      content: "üåô";
    }

    html, body {
      max-width: 100%;
      overflow-x: hidden;
      overflow-y: auto;
    }

    .instructions-container {
      margin-top: 3em;
      max-width: 700px;
      padding: 1em;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      border-radius: 12px;
    }

    body.dark .instructions-container {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    }

    .instructions-container p {
      font-size: 1.1em;
      line-height: 1.6em;
    }

    footer {
      margin-top: auto;
      padding: 2em 1em 1em;
      font-size: 0.9em;
      opacity: 0.8;
      width: 100%;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .footer-bottom {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 800px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      position: relative;
      margin-top: 1em;
    }

    .kofi-button-container {
      position: fixed;
      bottom: 1em;
      right: 1em;
      z-index: 1000;
    }

    .kofi-button-container a {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 0.3em 0.8em;
      font-size: 0.85em;
      border-radius: 6px;
      background-color: #3498db;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      transition: background-color 0.3s;
    }

    .kofi-button-container a:hover {
      background-color: #2980b9;
    }

    body.dark .kofi-button-container a {
      background-color: #333;
      color: #f0f0f0;
    }

    body.dark .kofi-button-container a:hover {
      background-color: #444;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <!-- Dark Mode Toggle -->
  <div class="dark-mode-toggle">
    <label class="toggle-switch">
      <input type="checkbox" id="darkModeSwitch">
      <span class="slider"></span>
    </label>
  </div>

  <h1>Overlay Setup Instructions</h1>

  <div class="instructions-container">
    <p>To display your live giveaway on stream:</p>
    <ol style="text-align: left;">
      <li>Open OBS Studio.</li>
      <li>Click the <strong>+</strong> button under <strong>Sources</strong>.</li>
      <li>Select <strong>Browser</strong> and click <strong>OK</strong>.</li>
      <li>Paste your Overlay URL into the <strong>URL</strong> field.<br>It looks like: <code>https://thesimplegiveaway.com/overlay/your-code</code></li>
      <li>Set the width to <strong>1920</strong> and height to <strong>1080</strong>.</li>
      <li>Click <strong>OK</strong> to add it to your scene.</li>
    </ol>
    <p>Now, when you run a giveaway, entries and winners will appear on your stream automatically!</p>
  </div>

  <footer>
    <div class="footer-bottom">
      <p style="margin: 0 auto;">Created by Robssuttie123</p>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <!--
  <div class="kofi-button-container">
    <a href="https://ko-fi.com/thesimplegiveaway" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
      üéÅ Support Hosting and Development
    </a>
  </div>
  -->

  <script>
    const isDark = localStorage.getItem('darkMode') === 'true';
    if (isDark) {
      document.body.classList.add('dark');
      document.getElementById('darkModeSwitch').checked = true;
    }

    document.getElementById('darkModeSwitch').addEventListener('change', function () {
      if (this.checked) {
        document.body.classList.add('dark');
        localStorage.setItem('darkMode', 'true');
      } else {
        document.body.classList.remove('dark');
        localStorage.setItem('darkMode', 'false');
      }
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>
